'Zona 3'

00:19:00.040 --> 00:19:01.400
'Berita terkini.'

00:19:01.560 --> 00:19:04.360
'Seekor harimau ganas sedang
mencari mangsa selama musim panas.'

00:19:04.640 --> 00:19:08.640
'Harimau ganas itu terlihat
di Zona 3 suaka margasatwa.'

00:19:09.920 --> 00:19:10.920
'Zona 3.'

00:19:12.400 --> 00:19:13.400
'Zona 3.'

00:19:17.600 --> 00:19:18.960
Saya akan segera kembali.

00:19:19.120 --> 00:19:20.840
Tapi mau kemana, Bu?

00:19:21.880 --> 00:19:23.200
Saya ingin pergi ke kamar kecil.

00:19:23.280 --> 00:19:24.400
Oke baiklah.

00:19:34.720 --> 00:19:35.720
'Zona 3.'

00:19:49.520 --> 00:19:51.040
'Zona 8.'

00:19:59.200 --> 00:20:00.200
'Zona 8.'

00:20:08.160 --> 00:20:09.160
'Zona 8.'

00:20:10.520 --> 00:20:11.520
Tulsi,

00:20:12.400 --> 00:20:14.520
bukankah kamu sangat
merindukan putrimu?

00:20:15.640 --> 00:20:16.760
Ini dia.

00:20:17.240 --> 00:20:19.840
Putri Anda akan segera
mendatangi Anda.

00:20:20.840 --> 00:20:22.240
Apakah kamu bahagia sekarang?

00:20:25.240 --> 00:20:26.400
'Zona 8.'

00:20:58.640 --> 00:21:01.000
Mungkinkah itu harimau?